{
  "stem": "2830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The conditions are better, let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians were coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The gypsies, they were already taken care of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The gypsies were out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so for us, I was there until-- then I went with that Czech, a lady.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- she helped me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She is a political prisoner, because she didn't agree with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they put her to, you know, into Birkenau because--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was from a high class family, very, very wealthy in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent her to Birkenau Auschwitz, because she didn't agree.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She took me-- she took me in the high commander.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it didn't-- I-- apparently I didn't talk too long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was already to the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I worked in the SS Commander where they cleaned the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she had about 20 of them she picked, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we marched up when all the commanders marched out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were the last ones to march out, only 20 of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she used to-- he picked it that one of be the SS high, the highest ranks, you know, that took care.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe next to Mengele, he is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He picked her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he picked her on a roll call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He saw her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was allowed to wear civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they didn't shaved her hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had beautiful, like a chestnut color hair, the most beautiful woman I've ever seen in my life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she received packages, every week a package from home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she used to give me a little garlic or some things, you know, a little bit of something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she took me under her wings, and my-- my feet started, you know, the wound--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--started a little better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I could walk better.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
